{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8fd315c175","title":"人民公社办工业（木刻）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a011054698","index":0,"year":1959,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"8fd315c175"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","name":"红旗一九五九年第三期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"07bb4374bf","name":"莫测"}]},"publication_details":{"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"721852f8b1","type":"paragraph","text":"去外地学习，群众推荐票有技术人才和以","index":0,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"f19418a000","type":"paragraph","text":"少的融，有的人主张越小越好，越士师带徒等方法，尤其是老工人和技术人具","index":1,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"fe991c4812","type":"paragraph","text":"越好。有的人则公开提出三不办，有集体研究，对关赞间烟进行苦心错研，解","index":2,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"21c52d0693","type":"paragraph","text":"动方机械不办；有象样的厂房不办；决了生产中很多难政解决的技术间题。如","index":3,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"ebe5b43fb5","type":"paragraph","text":"有工程师、技术具不办。看起来，这两种旧城人民公社信制造凝机的烘缸，很多工","index":4,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"a5e5f6b51b","type":"paragraph","text":"思想是代表着两个极端，而实际上却来自","index":5,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"3247f1ee10","type":"paragraph","text":"一个根源，即是脱离实际、脱离群众。这人过去从来没有见到过，当第一次筹烘缸失收以后，老工人卢万起合起三天吃不","index":6,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"29889c2a6e","type":"paragraph","text":"都会对发展公社工业产生有害的影响。各下饭。经过苦心研，发现水温度，","index":7,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"1fb2f60d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"极党委针对这些思想，进行了批制，并坚","index":8,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"4553fae29d","type":"paragraph","text":"持了“以小为主、中小精合”，“以士为口、砂型等主要关缝存在着间题，真改进之后，整子将适抵烘红斜成了，疏璃寺","index":9,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"52515ab927","type":"paragraph","text":"主、土祥洁合”，“土法先上马、土中出洋","index":10,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"4d8df83414","type":"paragraph","text":"的做法。人民公社路广法创的米机也是经过多次失收，楼于试制成功，而且效果良好，","index":11,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"680ed7f8dd","type":"paragraph","text":"由于坚持了以上的做法，这次运动中十二小时可碳米一万二千斤。","index":12,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"c89b7432ac","type":"paragraph","text":"所办的工业，便具有了“投责少、收效快、在建厂过程中，经过到不少原材料","index":13,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"b996ca064e","type":"paragraph","text":"设备制造简单”等等特点，因面群众就易缺乏的困难，趣过群众集体研究以后，根据","index":14,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"6e4ad04494","type":"paragraph","text":"于发撑自力更生办工业的积极性，他们在材料的性能、作用，也都找到了代用品。","index":15,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"4a538772da","type":"paragraph","text":"办工厂中主动提出了“没有物料自已找，例如，以白杨木代替红松木制造酒精蒸倍","index":16,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"14d7ee32d9","type":"paragraph","text":"凝有机器自已造，凝有技术积极学”，“自塔，以鲜地瓜代替麦获皮发酵制费，榨油厂用石磨代替螺旋榨的铁下拍等。","index":17,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-647d-4d48-ba9d-908ccd014457","articleId":"8fd315c175"},{"id":"0b7ebb598c","type":"paragraph","text":"群众很快地学会技术，并且有了不少创造发明，这也便得某些不相信群众的工程技术人具得到了有益的教育。","index":18,"publicationId":"e487fb9e-64